==English==
''Alternative spelling [[Phœnecian]]''

===Noun===
'''Phoenecian'''
# a native or inhabitant of [[Phoenecia]], a country on the eastern shores of the [[Mediterranean Sea]] in around 1000 BC.
# the [[semitic]] language spoken by the inhabitants of Phoencia.

===Adjective===
'''Phoenecian'''
# of or related to the country or [[civilisation]] of Phoenicia.

